description._content: Description: The Forest Guard's house Kioni, with terraces planted 1920 and onwards, in 1930, Machera Forest, Elevation about 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1930 Description: Terraces planted in 1919, with Cypress and Stone Pine trees, showing growth in 1927, Machera Forest, below Kioni Station, Elevation about 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1927 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
